parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear toe link can cause the vehicle to become unstable, leading to loss of control, accidents, and potential injuries.
symptoms: The rear end of the vehicle becomes unstable
the vehicle fishtails
the wheels misalign
the vehicle pulls to one side
the toe link breaks or snaps
the wheel sticks out
and the vehicle cannot be driven.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Lack of Mechanical Override for Rear Access Door
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The absence of a mechanical override or emergency release mechanism for the rear access door can lead to entrapment and potentially life-threatening situations in the event of a dead battery or electrical failure.
symptoms: The rear access door cannot be opened manually
the door is locked and cannot be opened without electricity
the door cannot be opened in an emergency situation.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A malfunctioning door latch can cause the door to not close or lock properly, compromising the safety and security of the vehicle's occupants and cargo.
symptoms: The door will not latch
the door will not close
the door will not lock
the door does not stay closed.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Sharp Metal Edge Causing Tire Damage
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sharp metal edge on the vehicle's body can cause tire damage and potentially lead to a loss of control or accident, especially when driving at low speeds.
symptoms: Tire damage or puncture
tire wear on the front right wheel
the vehicle's metal edge is exposed and can cause tire damage.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden loss of power steering functionality can cause the vehicle to become difficult or impossible to steer, increasing the risk of accidents and potentially leading to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power steering functionality while in motion
making it difficult or impossible to turn
the steering wheel becomes extremely hard to turn
the vehicle is difficult to control
and the driver may experience a sudden loss of steering ability.
